name    'Enrise-zendserver'
version '0.2.0'
source 'UNKNOWN'
author  'Dolf Schimmel (Freeaqingme) / Enrise - www.enrise.com'
license '3-Clause BSD license'
summary 'Installs Zend Server and fixes some paths to be more LSB compliant'
description 'Moves the log files to /var/log/zend, uses the /tmp partition, and allows to use puppet-based iptables configuration.
                Currently, this module supports Debian based systems only, although that should be easily extendible.
                This module was tested with Puppet version 2.7'
project_page 'http://www.github.com/Enrise/Puppet-Zendserver'

